---
title: Sizzlin’ Shrimp Bowls with Spicy Mayo plus Garlicky Roasted Asparagus & Sesame Seeds
description: Talk about a sizzle reel—these hearty shrimp bowls are loaded with craveable flavors and textures, so put down that takeout menu! You’ll top a bed of fluffy rice with garlicky seared shrimp and tender sautéed broccoli, drizzle that dynamic duo with savory-spicy mayonnaise for a boost of creaminess, then shower with nutty, crackly sesame seeds just before serving. Ready to be bowl-ed over?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/671fd84f97f1617b47570408-adb2bec3.jpeg
