author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sizzlin-shrimp-bowls-with-spicy-mayo-685bea630448900e51aa5f7d
servings: 2
time required: 20 minutes
course: main course
cuisine: East Asia
nutrition:
  calories: 620 kcal
